   <narrative xml:lang="EN">First Pediatric Hospice in South America</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We will build the first pediatric hospice where cancer and non-cancer children can live with their families in their final stage of life. With the technical advice of the EKR Chile Foundation, we will create a building of approximately 800 m2, where we will receive 9 children with their families so that a space for children entering palliative care.  We need to equip each building space according to the medical conditions indicated by the doctors.</narrative>
  </description>
